banner.banner-text: "Hello there! Hoping you are having a great day ... Welcome to '$(hostname)', your favorite IOSXR Sandbox"

route-policy.rpl-route-policy: route-policy PREP if destination in TEST1 then prepend as-path 420513140 prepend as-path 420513140 3 endif end-policy
route-policy TEST if destination in (1.1.1.0/24) then pass endif end-policy
route-policy RPL-1 if destination in TOTO then pass prepend as-path 1223 2 endif end-policy
route-policy TEST2 if destination in (2.2.2.0/24) then pass endif end-policy
route-policy TEST3 if destination in (3.3.3.0/24) then pass endif end-policy
route-policy TEST4 if destination in (4.4.4.0/24) then pass endif end-policy
route-policy filter if (as-path in path-1) then pass else drop endif end-policy
route-policy DEFAULT_ONLY_IPV6_POLICY if destination in DEFAULT_IPV6_NETS then pass endif end-policy
